  "title": "Keychain helper",
  "agent_type": "developer",
  "description": "Implement KeychainHelper.swift as a struct with two static methods: read(key: String) -> String? and write(key: String, value: String). Use kSecClassGenericPassword. write must upsert \u2014 attempt SecItemAdd first; on errSecDuplicateItem, fall back to SecItemUpdate. Errors are swallowed at this scale (nil on read failure, silent on write failure).",
